show.description: A powerful CEO is searching for one girl willing to submit to his rules. Dozens wait in line, but only one will be chosen for this secret contract. It’s not just a job, it’s a life of luxury, control, and emotional surrender. Behind closed doors, a dangerous game of power and passion begins. She must live by his word… or walk away from everything.
